vcdimager: vcdimager (GNU VCDImager)
vcdimager: 
vcdimager: VCDImager is a full-featured mastering suite for authoring, disassembling 
vcdimager: and analyzing Video CDs and Super Video CDs. It supports Video CD 1.1 
vcdimager: and 2.0 disc formats, Super Video CD 1.0 disc format, full playback 
vcdimager: control support, segment play items, automatic padding of MPEG 
vcdimager: streams on the fly, and support for 99-minute (out-of-specification) 
vcdimager: CD-R media.
